snippet.title: War Hospital | Commented Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
In War Hospital you play as Major Henry Wells, the head doctor of a military field hospital during the Great War. Daily life is all about resource management and difficult moral choices, so your ability to make the right decision under pressure will be put to the test. 

#WarHospital is scheduled for Early 2023 on PC, PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X|S.
